remarks: If two complex numbers are unequal, their quotient is not one. Contrapositive of ~ diveq1d .  (Contributed by David Moews, 28-Feb-2017.)
statement:
div1d.1 $e |- ( ph -> A e. CC ) $.
divcld.2 $e |- ( ph -> B e. CC ) $.
divcld.3 $e |- ( ph -> B =/= 0 ) $.
divne1d.4 $e |- ( ph -> A =/= B ) $.
divne1d $p |- ( ph -> ( A / B ) =/= 1 ) $.
